    "description": {
      "value": "<p>To use this technique, the target must be of the same size category as you, and you must wield the weapon used with two hands. The technique cannot be used on a moving (or falling) target. Make a melee attack against the target, which will deal 1d4 additional slashing damage per 2 levels (up to 5d4) on hit. In addition, the target is thrown upwards 1d3 x 5 ft, losing its Dexterity bonus to Defense and becoming unable to act until it starts falling on its next turn.</p>\n\n\n\n",
